title: 1: AI Heuristic
message:
1: AI Heuristic 

Implemented simple heuristic:

- Sum up the HP of the own units
- Sum up total HP of all units
- evaluation = ownHp / totalHp (making it a number between 0 and 1)
- if the game state is a winning game state
evaluation = 1 + 1 / #moves
guarantees that a winning move with the least number of moves is
preferably chosen

Task-Url: https://github.com/TyrfingX/TyrLib/issues/1
